data.description: Fixer upper or build your dream home on this 1 plus acre level lot. Large hardwood trees and multiple fruit trees enhance the property. Home is 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom with a large cinder block 2 car garage. 2 window a/c units cool the home. Home is currently on propane but natural gas is available at the street. Septic system will need updated as well as the roof. Come check it out and image the potential this home and lot have to offer.
